ere x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFv2kgQ%2FSuj6E4HXEJsk5DCiQ%2BE0DYqvVYkd9WpVHSxx3gv611rdx2HpvnvN2tDgAB3lQ4JYTyzb2bezL7dx6MIY5YLO1ARHnWPTk%2Bh1%2BvBrWZcglUQavZtQQ%2BFhEkeeP4ZFEqL6J5jAYU%2FDabn0%2Fb0AmrGqgwu6m7xRBJI35g8zSxXEsKEsLrgQca0ChPOhIPyOwH4EDM9ZQVbTJM8ZdKsDAEwyVMmzNSoFIuE2ZXl%2FNmSMmuRVk%2BFera2weRxjJrL%2BTRWYW4wWpkuIEVmp%2FSlRZlWM4FpmemQhQmwdbrcAIOPC5vQc8wFAhGxNptTsC4dFkXmGDQSe1yiAaVLMI0nVCVLkaJwQ%2B9tghUBvxiIcxmWGL9BqNJMGUpz7UBrZYSESK%2B4KdGMZTJiQkmElNojmvD1mf3h%2FVeXqluODxmGlhbeM5EjqLhEWDeqWYJdorEwyxeQuzBuocHNwrpwk2ieZvAJBbUF4aNWfxNutfrN8PfhuH87vILZAuYoURORzWyxmgqMuN2iqUHGY5DUmzIZxyQhlVhXXBMuIHWKfohmdC1Qek4cZZQC0wuYUYiYh5yej%2BFy%2BPrDeEgcaCZKhAL5PLFEHzEilJvThH%2BtOifUXCpNEwId72cYXENNaar3RMUnKZtLbvMI4fLD7XBQp3yMyrN33IYJyismFh9R%2F2Ei6MHjRAJkqDKBb1FkGD1bvKZ37gJ6zXPnU6AQM6RM3lALHUTl4vmVj%2Bc7p1DlkgYiZqHNmbhk8u7PslPOtXUgUmMPdANqPpwcgqtP5NNEzqOtQlwu3tkyGS%2BYSJbGOw6tZUVeQOkynu44rKoJqGabiC273wyc9eyC2CyybVPgec52cUZJTGTBRTTL52bbp135vApKHyZEjNGeXvTnmoekUznNwIBZZqxWWYLkNUBJb1fEt5aplt0R%2FB7NDbsvWb1SQjB9HW%2BsrtaU%2BQfOP6rijnjsTC2vjDzg91zwb8zN9VBGriEEK3dgVnNRtpx2%2F91NQttojKnajO9KxhO%2FrJkevI7zjnOqAF3Vpm9vLLtzkL63%2FpTe3ovPD%2FLS%2BG8aGluV%2F%2FpjqD9CTONfiGjsKbscYdLAQqk9Q%2FAwJrAxRnm4S2hrSagf%2FD9C98c4mGt1hHwurvqjv4AY1k6HM9LXn750N3Ut2tI8y9Pl2bDWtFCRkRSP%2BH2h37ScvThOIcutcdLJnT6bULlzowefXQWPQJscuzA5GqmQdNBpHNxVIjc5OoYieia26w5FWdurgnUqmuSJpqF2UqpI66LT8tt1eDrejuKaXkm6WOzH39SkHdh2u3PmBfth6SgS4G4WVLTmdgG1%2FvvX9f1BtoTNRVnHaLe94JW%2FG6J%2F%2FR5OYbDEHkqrMaNTGHNtEp4dCLMpjy%2BLOW%2BdvzrbjXNLjX7rLjgII2TzHPdDbylrBd3ptHfQ9h%2FTBzq7qcgVpNdp7UB%2BImWme44hHAO1pEo1owsDzWOE5gDju3q%2BjLAboD8avR5eHWD0heSXIHt6BYbF6GZgXOkDjOkGw3SYHEhvR0bWwF%2FcxtV0cLobWA9G3NimRtq9BmvlH6O0vVzUqo11DI%2FfH77DQ3MjxlOdjtuZu1L1YAn02fuy1IPbvZey27fXN%2BtN3YXyWsuJ8NnqZkZywSkLQ1t6455HEZzHZvSJPHr6B8vV74Q%3D" id="w1_2_5_6_7"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#eec2a8;strokeColor=#c65a2e;fontColor=#5a2a10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1261" y="956" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Net-negative lives&lt;br&gt;(animal suffering dominates)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Benatar)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem + net_negative_animal_lives&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The net-negative-lives hypothesis: factory-farmed and wild animals endure more suffering than wellbeing, so their lives are not worth living. Reducing that suffering is worth more per dollar (you are mitigating a catastrophe, not improving a good life), most of all for the astronomical wild-invertebrate populations. Combined with the meat-eater problem it drives human charities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVn9v2zYQ%2FSqHYMMcL3EkObETD%2F7Dcdw2mLsWTrZhqAuVlk4WF4oUSCqOm%2Ba77yjZ8e%2BtwAwYlnXHd3fvyMd7PooxYYWwfRXjUefo7Ay63S7ca8YlWAWRZl%2Fn9DCTMC4Czz%%2FuIHJHKYoURPXjXy%2B3DoYc7tBU52MJyCpfWUyjklCKrFuuCZcQGom%2FRDN6Fqg9JQ4yikFpucwoRAJjzg9n8D14M2H0YA40EyUCDPk09QSfcSIUG4zp%2FxL1TmhplJpajFceT9C%2FxZqSlO9pyo5zdhUclvECNcf7gf9Y8rHqCL%2FldsoRXnDxPwj6t9NDF14HkuAHFUu8B2KHONXi9fwLlxAr3HhfGYoxAQpk7fUQgdRuXh%2B5eP5zilShaQNkbDIFkxcM%2FnwR9kp59o8EKm%2BB7oONR9OD8Edj%2BXLWE7jjUJcLt75IhkvGE