ities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVm1T4zYQ%2Fis7TDsNKQTbvKeTDyGEg2muxwTamw5hgmKvYxVZ8kgyJsfx37uyE5KQ5MpM8wXhXT27%%2BFaq38It9r9qftHt9%2B%2B7Z7DaAJjlKiZxUY2mR0OjLhdoqlOxh2Q1KIyGcckIZVY51wTLiA1jP4QzehaoPSYOMooBaYnMKIQMQ85rXfgrHvxpd8lDjQTJUKBfJxYoo8YEcod14Q%2FVJ0TaiyVphbDqfczdK6gpjTVu6vi3ZSNJbd5hHD25bbb2aZ8jMqz37kNE5TnTEyuUf9pImjBy0ACZKgygZcoMozeLF7DO3QBvcah8ylQiBFSJp%2BohQ6icvH8ysfznVOockkHImahzZk4Y%2FLxr7JTznV%2FQ6T6Gug61HzY3QS3PZCvAzmOlgpxuXgH02S8YCBZGq847E8r8gJKl%2FF0xWFWTUA120Qs2f1G4KwHx8RmkS2bAs9ztuMDSmIgCy6iUT42yz5Hlc9JUPowIWKM1vSiPdY8JLnK6Qx0mGXGapUlSF4dlPR1Rvz%2BNNWyO%2BWU37CnktVzJQTTV%2FHC7mpPmX%2Fg%2FKMqbo%2FHzrTvlZE7%2FIkL%2Fo25c92VkWsIwcoVmNm5KFtO0%2F94k9AY9TFVi%2FFdybjrlzXTwjt13nFOFaCr2rTtjWWPDtL35r%2FS23v3%2ByAv9f%2Bmob5U%2Ba8fQ%2F0IMfUfEFFfU3Z5hEkDC6XWHILnPoH1McrDVUL3p4T6wf8jdH2MjblWV8hdcd7u%2FQ3EsHY6nJG%2B%2FnTfXNS1aEnzLE%2Bnd8Nc00JFRlI84vedftN29u5WhSy3xkknd%2FpsQuXujRbcuQpegIYcmzDY6qmQdNBpHDxWIjfY2oEieiO2CSkyWVurgttUNMkTvO4sg7oeVwouJuvhFiXoRyh00QhwzwcqSXM7gVr788X2eswl2XKgq5Dtq8%2BwB50pVldajRndqZhrk%2FBsA%2Byi2G3K9Zb6dOmeKQg9ZOMc12MtCaPD8hun9P54j7b%2Blt3QmEVBrdILjk9XIL%2BSsNIzxRCOgVpSpZrRfU%2FHKUKzgdJVOa4i%2BIer1PZ6F93zDRS%2BU%2BwSZE1zwLAYXZP71XhDnx4gTIfJhvRWVGAOfO%2FmTtO95x5QLehxYxsaafgM1sp%2FjNL2bFKr5mIHXr4%2Ff4fnxkKM1226LUfuRdSCKdCddz8d59u1b6rby6ub%2BUw2oXycciJ8NHtY0bRzysLQRC480yiC81iMPpBbr%2F8CKjTmvg%3D%3D" id="w1_2_5_6_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxG