armful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 net_negative_animal_lives → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVm1z4jYQ%2Fis7mXYKNHFskxdChw%2BEkLvMcb0bkvamc9xwwl5jNbLkkeQQLpf%2F3pUNAQK0N1O%2BRPGunt19Vnq0TwcxJqwQtqdiPGgfHB9Dp9OBO824BKsg0uzbnBYzCaMi9IMTmCkt4geOM5gF43B8Om6NgwBqxqocgqDuto8kwXSNKbLcciUhSgmtDT7kTKso5Uw4sOAihAASpsdsxubjtMiYNEtDCEzyjAkzNirDWcrs0nL6YsmYtUi7x0K9WFsg0Y4lTpnlDziuXMeC1i%2FQlK1RXCxspky2z6IU2CpjboDBx7lNaZ1wgUBsrMzmGKzLiMWxOQSNRCGXFEDpEkzjERXKMqTsuKHvNsWKg18MJIWMSozfIFJZrgyX05UD7ZUxEiJ94lVqxjIZM6EkQkY9Eh58fWlB%2F%2BGrS9Vtx8ccI0sbH5goEFRSIqy65ZVgl2gsTIo5FC6M22hwvbA23KaaZzl8QkGdQfio1d%2BEW%2B1%2B0%2F%2B9P%2Bze9a9gMocpStTMopfPl0cDY243aGqQ8RAktadMxjFJSCXWFdeEC5gk7g%2FRjK4FSk%2BJo5xSYHoOEwqR8IjT%2BhAu%2B9cfhn3iQDNRIsyQT1NL9BEjQrnDmvKvVeeEmkqlqbtw4f8MvRuoKU31HqnkKGNTyW0RI1x%2BuOv36pSPUUX%2BjtsoRXnFxPwj6j9MDB14GkmAHFUu8C2KHOMXi%2B%2F5py6g7506nxkKMUHK5A210EFULn5Q%2BfiBc4pUIelAJCyyBROXTN7%2FWXbKuTb3RGrsgG5ALYCjfXD1kXweyWm8UYjLxT9ZJOOHI8myZMuhuajIDyldxrMth2U1IdVsU7FhD7zQWU%2FOic1ZvmkKfd%2FZzk8oiZGccRFPiqnZ9DmrfFph6cOESDDe0YvuVPOIxKqgM9BjlhmrVZ4iefVQ0tcl8c1FqmV3yst%2Fyx5KVq%2BUEEzfJGu7qz1l%2FqHzj6u4A544U9MvI%2Ff4Axf8G3Pnui9j1xCClVswy3NRtpxu%2F%2F1tStdoiJlaj%2B9KxqOgrJkW%2FoXzTgqqAF3VpmtvLbt3kIG%2F%2BpXe%2FqvfD%2FLS%2BG8aGhuV%2F%2FpjqD9CTONfiGjsKLs8wqSBM6V2HILHIYENMS6ibUKbC0KD8P8RujvG3lyrJ%2BTz7Ko7%2BAuIYe10OCd9%2FelLe13X4g3NszxbvA0rTYsUGUnxiN9X%2Bk3b2asXFfLCGied3OmziZR7Nzrw2VXwBHTJsQ2jg4GKSAedxsF9JXKjg0OYxS%2FEtiFDJms7VbBORQd0FmpHZ6HXarbO6vB8uInv2l2JuZjvRl5XoxVgEPhe6%2BJ0NyA9PwLcREGFam7nUOu%2Bv67vht8QszV8%2F6LptU628bs37%2BEYegvgvrQac3p2sdAm5fmeGOt6uIrRap17Z63z7Rh31NW3bqBBGCCbFrgbdkNGHazvnZ2dbKHtfpP3tHFdfitIImIL8hPJMA01hnAM1NIq1ZymAzp8MZo9VG%2BL9yLC6TbLg8F1%2F2oPm6%2F0vQTZ0ScwLEHX%2FGElBjCkcYXpKN2T3pZmrIC%2FuFuq6ZV041YHBtxYTyNdVYO18h%2BjtL2c16pbdAhP3x%2B%2Fw6O3FuO5Tm%2FrxM1PHVgAffa%2FLC