 + meat_eater_problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The meat-eater problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFv4kYQ%2FSujqFWBJsSGJCRUfCCEu4uO60Uk7ak6Ttxij%2FE2611rdx2Hy%2BW%2Fd9aGAMG0JxUJYTyzb2bezL7dp4MQI5YJO1AhHnQPjo%2Bh1%2BvBnWZcglUQaPZtQQ%2B5hEnW8vwTyJUW4QPHHHJ%2F2pqeTTtQM1al0Km7pRNJEH1jsiS1XEkIYkLqggcp0yqIORMOyL9ogQ8R01OWs8U0zhImzcrQAiZ5woSZGpVgHjO7spyByaIINZfzaaSCzGC4MnUgQWan9EU9TbWaCUyKXIYsiIGtE%2BIGGNwsbEzPERcIVOjabI7BuoAsDM0haCR2uEQDShdgGo%2BoDpYgReGG3tsYyxJ%2FMRBlMigwfoNAJakylObagdbKEAmRXnFToBnLZMiEkggJ0S%2Ba8PWF3eHDV5eqW46PKQaWFj4wkSGoqEBYN6JZgF2isTDLFpC5MG6hwc3CunBHWO8c0wgjZPMMy4Vvh78Px%2F274RXMFjBHiZo4bKaLVcMx5HaLoQYZD0EqW%2BbhSCSkAuuKa0oVkJpEP8QwOvaVnhM9qaam6gXMKETEA07Ph3A5fPNxPKTyNRMFQo58HltijsgQyo1gzL%2BWTRNqLpWmwYAL72cYXENNaSr1SEVHCZtLbrMQ4fLj3XBQp3yMytL33AYxyismFjeo%2FzAh9OBpIgFSVKnAdyhSDF8sXtM7dQG95qnzyVGIGVImb6l7DqJ08fzSx%2FOdU6AySbMQscBmTFwyef9n0STn2t4TqVEB3YCaD0f74OoT%2BTyR83CrEJeLd7JMxmtNJEuiHYf2siKvRekynuw4rKppUc02Flt2v9ly1pMOsZmn26aW5zlb54SSmMici3CWzc22z1npc94qfJgQEYYVvejPNQ9IgjKagQGzzFit0hjJa4CS3q6Iby9TLboj%2BAOaW%2FZQsHqlhGD6OtpYXa4p8m85%2F7CMO%2BKRM7W9IvKAP3DBvzE310MZuoYQrNyBWc1F0XLa%2BPe3MdM